column1: #: description: The rapidity dependence of the inclusive JPsi nuclear modification factor obtained in p-Pb and Pb-p collisions. The first uncertainty is statistical
column2: the second one is the uncorrelated systematic uncertainty
column3: while the third one is the partially correlated systematic uncertainty. The fourth is a global uncertainty common to p-Pb and Pb-p results.
